(1, 'Privacy & Policy', 'privacy-policy', '<p class=\"mb-30\">Welcome to Eduman, a school management application developed by BDevs. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our Application. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By accessing or using our Application, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by all the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>1.1 Personal Information:</strong>\r\n<p>We may collect personal information that you provide directly to us, such as your name, contact information, email address, and other details when you register an account or use certain features of the Application.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>1.2 Usage Information:</strong>\r\n<p>We automatically collect certain information about how you interact with our Application, including your IP address, device information, browser type, operating system, and usage patterns. This information is used to analyze trends, administer the Application, and track user activities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>1.3 Cookies and Tracking Technologies:</strong>\r\n<p>We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience and collect information about your usage of the Application. Cookies are small files that are stored on your device and help us improve the functionality and security of the Application.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>2.1 Provide and Improve Services:</strong>\r\n<p>We may use the collected information to provide, maintain, and improve our Application, including enhancing user experience, personalizing content, and developing new features. We may also use the information to respond to your inquiries, fulfill your requests, and provide you with technical support.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>2.2 Communication:</strong>\r\n<p>We may use your contact information to communicate with you regarding updates, announcements, newsletters, promotional materials, and other relevant information related to the Application. You can opt-out of receiving these communications at any time.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>2.3 Aggregated Data:</strong>\r\n<p>We may anonymize and aggregate the collected information to generate statistical or demographic data that does not identify any individual. This aggregated data may be used for various purposes, including research, analytics, and improving our services.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>3. How We Share Your Information</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>3.1 Third-Party Service Providers:</strong>\r\n<p>We may engage third-party service providers to perform functions on our behalf, such as hosting, data analysis, customer support, and marketing. These service providers will have access to your personal information only to the extent necessary to perform their functions and are obligated to maintain its confidentiality.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>3.2 Legal Compliance and Protection:</strong>\r\n<p>We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities. We may also disclose your information to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property, or that of our users or others.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>3.3 Business Transfers:</strong>\r\n<p>In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets, your information may be transferred as part of the transaction. We will notify you via email or a prominent notice on our Application of any change in ownership or the use of your personal information.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>4. Data Security</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\">\r\n<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, please be aware that no security measure is completely foolproof, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>5. Children\'s Privacy</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\">\r\n<p>Our Application is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age. If you become aware that your child has provided us with personal information without your consent, please contact us, and we will promptly remove such information from our systems.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>6. Your Choices</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\">\r\n<p>You have the right to access, update, correct, and delete your personal information. You may also choose to disable cookies</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'Privacy & Policy', 'Meta Description', 'images/course_1/2P26dB8nSZRZ0o4jwUfR3nDQDuz6prHhSj4vGmj7.jpg', 'Active', '2023-05-04 08:35:02', '2023-05-07 06:02:42'),
(2, 'Refund Policy', 'refund-policy', '<p class=\"mb-30\">Thank you for choosing Eduman, a school management application developed by BDevs. We strive to provide you with a seamless and satisfying experience. However, we understand that circumstances may arise where you may require a refund. This Refund Policy outlines our guidelines and procedures regarding refunds. By accessing or using our Application, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by the terms of this Refund Policy.</p>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>1. Eligibility for Refunds</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>1. Subscription Plans:</strong>\r\n<p>If you have subscribed to one of our paid subscription plans, you may be eligible for a refund under the following circumstances:</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>a. Technical Issues: </strong>\r\n<p>If you experience significant technical difficulties that prevent you from accessing or using the Application despite reasonable attempts to resolve the issue with our support team.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>b. Dissatisfaction with Service:</strong>\r\n<p>If you are not satisfied with the features, functionalities, or performance of the Application, and you request a refund within a specified period from the date of subscription.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>2. Refund Request Procedure</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>2.1 Contacting Customer Support::</strong>\r\n<p>To initiate a refund request, please contact our customer support team at <a href=\"https://support.bdevs.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://support.bdevs.net/</a>. Please provide the following details:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Your name and contact information</li>\r\n<li>Subscription details (such as plan type, duration, and purchase date)</li>\r\n<li>Reason for the refund request</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>2.2 Evaluation Process:</strong>\r\n<p>Once we receive your refund request, our customer support team will review the request and assess its eligibility based on the criteria mentioned in Section 1. We may require additional information or clarification during the evaluation process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>2.3 Refund Determination:</strong>\r\n<p>The decision regarding the refund will be at our discretion and will depend on the specific circumstances of the request. We will notify you of our decision within a reasonable timeframe.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>3. Refund Options</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>3.1 Refund Method:</strong>\r\n<p>If your refund request is approved, we will process the refund using the original payment method you used for the subscription purchase.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>3.2 Refund Amount:</strong>\r\n<p>The refund amount will depend on the remaining unused portion of your subscription period. We reserve the right to deduct any applicable transaction fees or charges incurred during the refund process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>4. Non-Refundable Items</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>4.1 Non-Refundable Circumstances:</strong>\r\n<p>Please note that the following circumstances are generally not eligible for refunds:</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>a. Free Trials: </strong>\r\n<p>Refunds are not provided for free trial periods or any promotional offers explicitly labeled as non-refundable.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\"><strong>b. Change of Mind: </strong>\r\n<p>Refunds will not be granted solely based on a change of mind or personal preferences unrelated to the Application\'s performance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>5. Modification of Refund Policy</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\">\r\n<p>We reserve the right to modify or update this Refund Policy at any time. Any changes to this policy will be effective immediately upon posting the revised version on our Application. We encourage you to review this Refund Policy periodically for any updates.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>6. Contact Us</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\">\r\n<p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Refund Policy or wish to submit a refund request, please contact our customer support team at [contact information]. We will be happy to assist you and address any queries you may have.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-childd\"><strong>Note: </strong>\r\n<p>This Refund Policy is provided for informational purposes only and does not constitute a binding contract or legal advice.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'Refund Policy', 'Meta Description', 'images/course_1/OjczCMJoleet9n7NSrauB8eBRXHlTUDnIplWJMko.jpg', 'Active', '2023-05-07 06:40:43', '2023-05-07 06:40:43'),
