d-party websites or resources. Bdevs does not endorse or assume responsibility for any content, products, or services provided by such third parties. Your interactions with these third parties are solely between you and the third party, and Bdevs shall not be liable for any damages or losses arising from such interactions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item mb-30\">\r\n<h4>5. Limitation of Liability</h4>\r\n<div class=\"single-info-item-child\">\r\n<p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, BDevs and its affiliates, officers, directors, employees, agents, and licensors shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to loss of profits, data.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'Terms & Conditions', 'Meta Description', 'images/course_1/M95PbYwQpVuYuFR5JuUKwelyJImGCVTtvjpjpXCq.jpg', 'Active', '2023-05-07 08:55:22', '2023-05-07 08:55:22');